\frac{\mathrm d}{\mathrm dc}\left(\int_{-\infty}^{c}F_X(x)\mathrm dx - \int_{c}^{\infty}(1-F_X(x))\mathrm dx\right)=F_X(c)-(-1)(1-F_X(c))=1.
